1
00:00:11,458 --> 00:00:16,333
If I am slain here today...
the world will be led into ruin.

2
00:00:17,666 --> 00:00:20,375
That does not concern me...

3
00:00:20,458 --> 00:00:21,916
My task is a simple one,

4
00:00:22,000 --> 00:00:27,250
to take your life just as
I was ordered... Die... Luna.

5
00:00:30,125 --> 00:00:32,916
[CASSHERN GRIMACES 
AND BUILDS TO A ROAR]

6
00:02:55,291 --> 00:02:58,458
What... did you say?

7
00:02:58,541 --> 00:03:02,958
It's because...
you are... Casshern.

8
00:03:05,250 --> 00:03:07,583
Casshern?

9
00:03:07,666 --> 00:03:09,166
Yes.

10
00:03:09,250 --> 00:03:11,833
[DIO] One who cannot
contain himself in battle...

11
00:03:11,916 --> 00:03:13,083
[DIO] One who cannot feel peace

12
00:03:13,166 --> 00:03:16,000
until every living
thing is destroyed...

13
00:03:16,083 --> 00:03:18,958
It all stems from
who you are, Casshern.

14
00:03:19,041 --> 00:03:21,083
Casshern.

15
00:03:21,166 --> 00:03:22,750
Casshern

16
00:03:26,875 --> 00:03:28,958
You were created...

17
00:03:29,041 --> 00:03:31,666
...to take every
lifeform on this planet

18
00:03:31,750 --> 00:03:34,416
and turn it to dust.

19
00:03:35,791 --> 00:03:37,791
For that purpose?

20
00:03:38,625 --> 00:03:40,291
You are different...

21
00:03:40,375 --> 00:03:42,750
...from robots and humans.

22
00:03:45,166 --> 00:03:47,083
Who are you?

23
00:03:47,166 --> 00:03:50,000
How do you know
details of my life?

24
00:03:50,083 --> 00:03:52,833
[CASSHERN] What else
do you know about me?

25
00:03:53,583 --> 00:03:55,708
[DIO]
What else?

26
00:03:55,791 --> 00:03:59,000
Try everything there
is to know... about you.

27
00:04:08,250 --> 00:04:12,500
But see...
all that doesn't matter.

28
00:04:12,583 --> 00:04:15,833
Because you are going
to die here today.

29
00:04:15,916 --> 00:04:18,333
By my own hand.

30
00:04:21,041 --> 00:04:22,458
[METAL FOOT POUNDS THE GROUND]

31
00:04:22,541 --> 00:04:24,833
[ROBOT BANDIT 1] Not if I have
anything to say about it!

32
00:04:27,125 --> 00:04:28,000
[ROBOT 0]
Bandits!

33
00:04:28,083 --> 00:04:29,083
[ROBOT K]
They're still here?

34
00:04:29,166 --> 00:04:30,958
[ROBOT G]
Oh no!

35
00:04:31,958 --> 00:04:33,750
[OHJI]
Don't worry!

36
00:04:35,416 --> 00:04:38,416
It looks to me like
they're after Casshern.

37
00:04:40,125 --> 00:04:41,916
Be careful!

38
00:04:43,458 --> 00:04:45,208
[CASSHERN SURPRISED]

39
00:04:45,291 --> 00:04:48,166
[ROBOT 0]
That guy is Casshern

40
00:04:48,250 --> 00:04:50,916
[ROBOT BANDIT 1]
Casshern is ours.

41
00:04:51,000 --> 00:04:52,083
[ROBOT BANDIT 2]
He's our prey 

42
00:04:52,166 --> 00:04:54,625
and there's nothing
you can do about it!

43
00:04:54,708 --> 00:04:56,458
Their prey?

44
00:04:56,541 --> 00:04:59,958
[METAL STEPS POUND THE GROUND]

45
00:05:00,041 --> 00:05:02,000
[METALLIC LAUGH]

46
00:05:05,916 --> 00:05:09,041
[ROBOT BANDIT YELLS]

47
00:05:09,125 --> 00:05:10,916
[COLLISION AND FALL]

48
00:05:12,291 --> 00:05:16,333
[ROBOT GROWL]

49
00:05:16,416 --> 00:05:17,791
Friender.

50
00:05:18,708 --> 00:05:20,875
[ROBOT BANDIT 4]
Don't get in our way.

51
00:05:20,958 --> 00:05:22,416
You can't stop us!

52
00:05:22,500 --> 00:05:24,666
[METAL ON METAL CRUSHING]

53
00:05:30,541 --> 00:05:31,833
[RINGO REACTS SHOCKED]

54
00:05:31,916 --> 00:05:36,875
[VARIOUS METALS
COLLIDING DURING FIGHT]

55
00:05:53,791 --> 00:05:55,375
[DIO CHUCKLES SOFTLY]

56
00:05:55,458 --> 00:05:59,708
Oh wow... he's...
he's as strong as Casshern.

57
00:06:01,375 --> 00:06:03,791
Of course I am.

58
00:06:03,875 --> 00:06:06,291
Casshern and I both
share nearly identical

59
00:06:06,375 --> 00:06:08,166
power profiles.

60
00:06:10,541 --> 00:06:12,500
But the only thing is...

61
00:06:12,583 --> 00:06:15,166
...you don't know
how to use them.

62
00:06:18,750 --> 00:06:20,375
[DIO] With this power,
you could dominate

63
00:06:20,458 --> 00:06:22,625
everything on this planet.

64
00:06:24,291 --> 00:06:25,750
Just like...

65
00:06:25,833 --> 00:06:28,458
...Braiking Boss did before.

66
00:06:29,958 --> 00:06:32,333
So I will become the dominator

67
00:06:32,416 --> 00:06:35,458
and I will be unstoppable.

68
00:06:35,541 --> 00:06:38,791
I will...
change this world forever.

69
00:06:40,583 --> 00:06:44,583
Braiking Boss...? Is that?

70
00:06:49,000 --> 00:06:52,583
You honestly don't remember...?

71
00:06:52,666 --> 00:06:54,583
Not even me?!

72
00:07:06,708 --> 00:07:08,083
Ohji?

73
00:07:13,125 --> 00:07:14,083
You mean to tell me

74
00:07:14,166 --> 00:07:17,291
you've even
forgotten our destiny?

75
00:07:18,875 --> 00:07:23,458
Too bad...
I remember it clearly.

76
00:07:23,541 --> 00:07:28,625
I don't... remember a thing...

77
00:07:28,708 --> 00:07:31,125
Nothing about this world...

78
00:07:31,208 --> 00:07:32,333
...let alone what kind of

79
00:07:32,416 --> 00:07:35,625
involvement I may
have had with it.

80
00:07:35,708 --> 00:07:38,250
Well... I guess can help you

81
00:07:38,333 --> 00:07:40,291
with some of the grey areas...

82
00:07:40,375 --> 00:07:42,166
If you want.

83
00:07:45,791 --> 00:07:48,166
[DIO] Humans were no
match for robots...

84
00:07:48,250 --> 00:07:49,833
[DIO] They wiped humanity
off the planet

85
00:07:49,916 --> 00:07:51,291
and took their place of reign

86
00:07:51,375 --> 00:07:54,333
by becoming the new
rulers of the world.

87
00:07:55,666 --> 00:07:57,666
And the one in control...

88
00:07:57,750 --> 00:07:59,625
...was Braiking Boss.

89
00:08:03,250 --> 00:08:04,708
But then...

90
00:08:04,791 --> 00:08:08,708
...everything was led
to ruin after the death of Luna!

91
00:08:10,541 --> 00:08:12,000
Ruin.

92
00:08:14,125 --> 00:08:17,500
[DIO] We could do nothing
to stop its progress.

93
00:08:19,250 --> 00:08:23,208
But... I now have the
ability to stop the ruin.

94
00:08:23,291 --> 00:08:24,666
[RINGO AND OHJI
REACT SHOCKED] 

95
00:08:30,250 --> 00:08:32,458
[ROBOT R] You can
really end the ruin?

96
00:08:32,541 --> 00:08:34,125
[ROBOT J]
Is that true?

97
00:08:35,041 --> 00:08:36,833
The absolute truth...

98
00:08:36,916 --> 00:08:39,375
See once I have attained
world domination, I will be

99
00:08:39,458 --> 00:08:40,583
capable of granting the

100
00:08:40,666 --> 00:08:43,583
robotic race with eternal
life once again.

101
00:08:43,916 --> 00:08:46,125
[GROUP SIGHS WITH AWE]

102
00:08:46,208 --> 00:08:48,166
Eternal... life?

103
00:08:50,416 --> 00:08:52,041
[DIO]
But in order to do that...

104
00:08:52,125 --> 00:08:54,083
...I must kill you.

105
00:08:56,708 --> 00:08:57,916
Now...

106
00:08:58,000 --> 00:08:59,333
In exchange for your life

107
00:08:59,416 --> 00:09:01,833
every being in this
world will be saved...

108
00:09:01,916 --> 00:09:03,500
Casshern!

109
00:09:05,416 --> 00:09:06,916
Hold on.

110
00:09:07,000 --> 00:09:09,291
In exchange for my life?

111
00:09:33,458 --> 00:09:35,166
[ROBOT M]
The ruin!

112
00:09:35,250 --> 00:09:40,958
[CLANKING METAL
AND GHOSTLY MURMURS]

113
00:09:41,041 --> 00:09:42,416
[RINGO REACTS SCARED]

114
00:09:42,500 --> 00:09:44,333
[ROBOT M]
You can stop the ruin?

115
00:09:44,416 --> 00:09:46,375
[ROBOT R]
We don't have to die?

116
00:09:50,000 --> 00:09:54,250
[ROBOT G] So if Casshern dies...
then all of us will be saved?

117
00:09:58,333 --> 00:10:00,500
Casshern.

118
00:10:00,583 --> 00:10:02,291
Please save us.

119
00:10:02,375 --> 00:10:04,208
You have to.

120
00:10:04,291 --> 00:10:06,833
[ROBOT I]
Please... save us.

121
00:10:11,083 --> 00:10:13,083
[ROBOT K]
You have to do it!

122
00:10:16,875 --> 00:10:19,083
[RINGO SHUDDERS IN FEAR]

123
00:10:21,083 --> 00:10:23,458
Please, save us.

124
00:10:24,000 --> 00:10:25,791
[ROBOTS GROAN AND PLEAD]

125
00:10:25,875 --> 00:10:27,333
[ROBOT M]
Save us.

126
00:10:35,875 --> 00:10:38,500
Hear that... Casshern?

127
00:10:43,333 --> 00:10:46,000
Every one of them
is in search of salvation.

128
00:10:51,875 --> 00:10:53,458
If your life were to end

129
00:10:53,541 --> 00:10:55,791
not only would those
standing around us,

130
00:10:55,875 --> 00:10:58,125
but every living robotic
creature suffering from

131
00:10:58,208 --> 00:11:00,958
the ruin would
be saved from death.

132
00:11:03,000 --> 00:11:05,833
You were created in order
to annihilate all life yet

133
00:11:05,916 --> 00:11:09,833
you can redeem yourself
by sacrificing your own...

134
00:11:09,916 --> 00:11:13,083
Doesn't that sound wonderful?

135
00:11:13,166 --> 00:11:14,541
[CASSHERN]
So...

136
00:11:16,250 --> 00:11:17,416
If I die...

137
00:11:17,500 --> 00:11:19,750
...the world will be saved?

138
00:11:21,333 --> 00:11:24,208
Not exactly, I have to kill you
to discover the mechanisms

139
00:11:24,291 --> 00:11:28,041
that govern your life
for it to work.

140
00:11:28,125 --> 00:11:32,458
Really... why's that?

141
00:11:32,541 --> 00:11:35,791
You are the one who killed
Luna and began the ruin...

142
00:11:35,875 --> 00:11:38,166
...yet you don't show a
single sign of it anywhere

143
00:11:38,250 --> 00:11:39,791
on your body.

144
00:11:39,875 --> 00:11:42,458
So If I can
discover your secret...

145
00:11:42,541 --> 00:11:45,375
...then the world will be saved.

146
00:11:45,458 --> 00:11:47,333
[CASSHERN]
My secret?

147
00:11:48,541 --> 00:11:51,666
I'd like to know
the secret... for myself.

148
00:11:54,291 --> 00:11:56,000
I want to know
why I can't die.

149
00:11:56,083 --> 00:11:58,208
What makes me immortal?

150
00:11:59,875 --> 00:12:03,166
But if what you say is true,
and you can indeed kill me,

151
00:12:03,250 --> 00:12:07,041
then it doesn't really
matter in the end.

152
00:12:07,125 --> 00:12:08,708
Casshern.

153
00:12:09,375 --> 00:12:10,958
[OHJI SIGHS UNDER HIS BREATH]

154
00:12:11,958 --> 00:12:13,333
Now...

155
00:12:13,916 --> 00:12:17,000
You said that you and
I have identical powers.

156
00:12:19,416 --> 00:12:21,500
Maybe crossing paths with you...

157
00:12:21,583 --> 00:12:24,375
...is exactly what
I've been waiting for.

158
00:12:32,541 --> 00:12:35,125
Okay... Please kill me.

159
00:12:35,208 --> 00:12:36,916
Casshern!

160
00:12:37,000 --> 00:12:38,708
You don't have to ask.

161
00:12:38,791 --> 00:12:40,625
That's why I'm here.

162
00:12:40,708 --> 00:12:42,666
[LEDA CHUCKLES]

163
00:13:00,208 --> 00:13:01,833
[IMPACT EXPLOSION]

164
00:13:01,916 --> 00:13:03,083
[FRIENDER SNARLS]

165
00:13:11,791 --> 00:13:13,375
Friender!

166
00:13:33,666 --> 00:13:39,000
So Casshern... It seems wherever
you go you always find conflict.

167
00:13:40,458 --> 00:13:42,250
[BLAST]

168
00:13:50,333 --> 00:13:53,291
Please... Just end it.

169
00:13:55,541 --> 00:13:57,333
[DIO GRIMACES]

170
00:14:07,291 --> 00:14:09,000
[MASSIVE BLAST]

171
00:14:09,083 --> 00:14:11,666
[ROCK AND DEBRIS HIT THE GROUND]

172
00:14:17,041 --> 00:14:19,000
[EXPLOSION]

173
00:14:21,833 --> 00:14:23,416
[DIO]
What the?

174
00:14:33,000 --> 00:14:34,583
[DIO]
Damn you!

175
00:15:06,291 --> 00:15:08,250
[BLAST]

176
00:15:17,583 --> 00:15:20,166
[DIO]
I cannot lose to you...

177
00:15:22,208 --> 00:15:25,375
[DIO] Because I am the one
who will change the world...

178
00:15:25,458 --> 00:15:26,833
Now die!

179
00:15:34,916 --> 00:15:38,125
I won't let you...
kill Casshern.

180
00:15:48,083 --> 00:15:51,041
[LEDA CHUCKLES]

181
00:15:54,250 --> 00:15:56,041
Who was that?

182
00:16:00,333 --> 00:16:01,708
Well.

183
00:16:05,083 --> 00:16:08,750
Now's your chance to
avenge your sister's death.

184
00:16:17,166 --> 00:16:19,625
Don't misunderstand me...

185
00:16:19,708 --> 00:16:22,875
It's not like I don't
despise you anymore...

186
00:16:22,958 --> 00:16:25,625
...the next time our paths
cross I will kill you...

187
00:16:25,708 --> 00:16:27,208
...but it will be
a fair fight cause

188
00:16:27,291 --> 00:16:31,166
the last thing I want to do
is embarrass my sister's memory.

189
00:16:40,750 --> 00:16:44,416
[LYUZE] Until then you do not
have my permission to die,

190
00:16:53,291 --> 00:16:57,833
[CASSHERN GRIMACES IN PAIN]

191
00:16:57,916 --> 00:16:59,291
Casshern?

192
00:17:00,125 --> 00:17:05,083
[CASSHERN CONTINUES
TO GRIMACE IN PAIN]

193
00:17:15,500 --> 00:17:20,458
[DIO GRIMACES IN PAIN]

194
00:17:21,083 --> 00:17:22,458
[LEDA]
Dio.

195
00:17:33,666 --> 00:17:38,625
[WIND BLOWS AND CLOCKS TICK]

196
00:17:48,500 --> 00:17:50,333
[LEDA SIGHS]

197
00:18:13,000 --> 00:18:15,333
[RINGO]
Are you awake now?

198
00:18:16,208 --> 00:18:20,291
[CASSHERN]
Am I... alive?

199
00:18:20,375 --> 00:18:22,708
Friender's doing a
lot better too.

200
00:18:24,083 --> 00:18:25,708
Friender?

201
00:18:25,791 --> 00:18:29,750
[RINGO] That is his name,
right...? The doggy?

202
00:18:35,208 --> 00:18:37,833
Alright... now you're set boy.

203
00:18:42,458 --> 00:18:45,791
Thank goodness Ohji
was able to fix you doggy.

204
00:18:45,875 --> 00:18:49,708
Ohji... so you saved me?

205
00:18:49,791 --> 00:18:52,208
I didn't lay a finger on ya...

206
00:18:52,291 --> 00:18:54,000
Your body seemed to
find a way to heal your

207
00:18:54,083 --> 00:18:57,166
wounds on it's own.

208
00:18:57,250 --> 00:18:59,208
You're amazing.

209
00:19:00,791 --> 00:19:02,041
[RINGO]
That must have something

210
00:19:02,125 --> 00:19:04,916
to do with why you're
always so pretty looking,

211
00:19:13,500 --> 00:19:16,458
Always... on my own.

212
00:19:18,333 --> 00:19:20,541
Why can't I just die?

213
00:19:24,625 --> 00:19:25,666
The man I fought.

214
00:19:25,750 --> 00:19:27,416
Do you know what
happened to him?

215
00:19:27,500 --> 00:19:31,458
A strange looking lady
with long hair took him away.

216
00:19:31,541 --> 00:19:34,958
I see... I remember now.

217
00:19:41,041 --> 00:19:44,458
[CASSHERN] He said the world
could be saved if I died...

218
00:19:44,541 --> 00:19:48,250
He said he would discover
the secret of my body

219
00:19:48,333 --> 00:19:51,125
and why the ruin
doesn't affect me.

220
00:19:51,208 --> 00:19:52,791
And if that happens...

221
00:19:52,875 --> 00:19:57,708
I can die... and finally
atone for killing Luna.

222
00:19:57,791 --> 00:19:59,916
[OHJI]
Alright, that's enough.

223
00:20:03,833 --> 00:20:05,416
[OHJI]
Let's go.

224
00:20:08,000 --> 00:20:09,875
What about him?

225
00:20:11,750 --> 00:20:14,666
We'll surely be attacked again
if we're caught near him...

226
00:20:14,750 --> 00:20:17,875
We don't have enough
lives to spare for that.

227
00:20:23,916 --> 00:20:26,875
[CASSHERN] Do you know
anything about me?

228
00:20:34,208 --> 00:20:37,000
I can't be hurt...
Why is that?

229
00:20:37,083 --> 00:20:42,541
I have no idea... but...
from the rumors I've heard,

230
00:20:42,625 --> 00:20:45,833
Luna was also immortal.

231
00:20:45,916 --> 00:20:47,333
You did the impossible...

232
00:20:47,416 --> 00:20:49,875
...killing someone
who could not die...

233
00:20:49,958 --> 00:20:53,291
For all I know she may
have placed a curse on you.

234
00:20:58,583 --> 00:21:01,541
[CAR STARTING UP AND MOVING]

235
00:21:10,833 --> 00:21:13,791
The impossible... No way.

236
00:21:17,083 --> 00:21:20,250
Luna... was immortal too.

237
00:21:36,250 --> 00:21:39,458
[CASSHERN THINKS]
I have nothing to go off of...

238
00:21:39,541 --> 00:21:42,708
...but I still want to know...

239
00:21:42,791 --> 00:21:45,291
What was Luna...?

240
00:21:45,375 --> 00:21:47,375
And what am I?

241
00:22:02,291 --> 00:22:07,250
[CLOSING SONG]

242
00:23:34,708 --> 00:23:37,166
[CASSHERN] There was a woman
who built a tower...

243
00:23:37,250 --> 00:23:41,291
...saying "the world
still has beauty."

244
00:23:41,375 --> 00:23:42,833
[CASSHERN]
Next time,

245
00:23:42,916 --> 00:23:46,875
The Woman of the Tall Tower.

